## 실전 패턴

### 패턴 1: 안전한 Wrapper 작성

```rust
pub struct SafeBuffer {
    data: Vec<u8>,
}

impl SafeBuffer {
    pub fn read(&self, offset: usize) -> Option<u8> {
        if offset < self.data.len() {
            unsafe {
                Some(*self.data.as_ptr().add(offset))
            }
        } else {
            None
        }
    }
}
// 호출자는 안전함 (경계 검사 내포)
```

### 패턴 2: Memory Manager

```rust
pub struct Arena {
    memory: Vec<u8>,
    offset: usize,
}

impl Arena {
    pub fn allocate(&mut self, size: usize) -> Option<&mut [u8]> {
        if self.offset + size <= self.memory.len() {
            let ptr = &mut self.memory[self.offset];
            self.offset += size;
            unsafe {
                Some(std::slice::from_raw_parts_mut(ptr, size))
            }
        } else {
            None
        }
    }
}
```

### 패턴 3: FFI Boundary

```rust
extern "C" {
    fn external_function(x: i32) -> i32;
}

pub fn safe_call(x: i32) -> i32 {
    // 매개변수 검증
    if x < 0 || x > 1000 {
        return 0;
    }

    unsafe {
        external_function(x)
    }
}
```

